=The Antidote to Love=
=Episode 24=

2
00:01:13,140 --> 00:01:14,980
Thank you for all your help.

3
00:01:15,220 --> 00:01:16,240
If not for you,

4
00:01:16,380 --> 00:01:18,320
the Moon Clan's revival
wouldn't be so swift.

5
00:01:20,340 --> 00:01:21,780
Seeing you doing well,

6
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:23,440
I suppose it's time I go.

7
00:01:23,620 --> 00:01:24,460
Where will you go?

8
00:01:25,860 --> 00:01:26,780
Well,

9
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:30,900
I'll roam the vast lands freely

10
00:01:31,260 --> 00:01:34,980
and have the wind welcome me
even at the edge of the world.

11
00:01:41,690 --> 00:01:43,980
By the way, I'm curious.

12
00:01:46,460 --> 00:01:47,940
If I make a wish at the Sacred Pool,

13
00:01:51,060 --> 00:01:52,420
will my wish truly come true?

14
00:01:56,380 --> 00:01:58,030
This is our special coin.

15
00:01:58,660 --> 00:02:00,090
It can make your wish come true.

16
00:02:02,630 --> 00:02:03,960
When making a wish,

17
00:02:05,460 --> 00:02:06,940
a sincere heart is key.

18
00:02:07,060 --> 00:02:07,940
Give it a try.

19
00:02:36,820 --> 00:02:37,760
Do you feel it?

20
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:41,060
What?

21
00:02:45,540 --> 00:02:48,060
Maybe I wasn't sincere enough.

22
00:02:48,260 --> 00:02:49,100
Forget it.

23
00:02:49,660 --> 00:02:50,500
Bye.

24
00:02:58,290 --> 00:02:59,510
Be careful on your way.

25
