35
00:04:03,580 --> 00:04:04,620
It's my fault.

36
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:06,900
Zhe.

37
00:04:11,420 --> 00:04:12,540
Zhe.

38
00:04:13,900 --> 00:04:15,860
My child.

39
