40
00:04:22,820 --> 00:04:24,500
he once told me

41
00:04:25,780 --> 00:04:28,580
he'd give anything

42
00:04:29,220 --> 00:04:30,940
to have you become

43
00:04:31,740 --> 00:04:35,860
the eternal commander of the North Army

44
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:37,780
and the future sovereign.

45
00:04:39,340 --> 00:04:40,180
No.

46
00:04:40,860 --> 00:04:41,700
Father,

47
00:04:42,460 --> 00:04:44,220
