During my reign of over 20 years,

53
00:04:57,200 --> 00:05:00,420
I restored cities, opened granaries,

54
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:02,820
lessened taxes and labor,

55
00:05:03,180 --> 00:05:05,220
and aided the poor

56
00:05:05,710 --> 00:05:08,540
to free the people from famine.

57
00:05:09,580 --> 00:05:11,060
I hope Dawei

58
00:05:12,740 --> 00:05:14,740
