59
00:05:17,420 --> 00:05:18,260
Yes.

60
00:05:19,260 --> 00:05:21,500
You've achieved much,

61
00:05:21,700 --> 00:05:23,100
yet you failed the Moon Clan.

62
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:30,660
It was my greed

63
00:05:31,300 --> 00:05:33,220
that brought ruin to the Moon Clan

64
00:05:33,660 --> 00:05:35,500
and hurt you two.

65
00:05:39,740 --> 00:05:40,820
He.

66
00:05:44,260 --> 00:05:45,140
He.

67
00:05:45,940 --> 00:05:46,780
Come.

68
00:05:53,780 --> 00:05:54,780
Father.

69
