141
00:10:53,100 --> 00:10:53,970
Oh, right.

142
00:10:54,460 --> 00:10:55,500
Speaking of the Moon Clan,

143
00:10:55,920 --> 00:10:57,080
I have something to ask you.

144
00:10:57,140 --> 00:10:59,220
